       REPORT SECTION.
      *--------------
       COPY COLRFTOC.
           .
       COPY COLRTTOC.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      *==================
       DECLARATIVES.
       DEC-PH-TOC SECTION.
           USE BEFORE REPORTING PH-TOC.
       INI-PH-TOC.
       FIN-PH-TOC.
           EXIT.
       END DECLARATIVES.

       MAIN SECTION.
      *------------
       INI-MAIN.
       COPY GNSBGEDB.
           MOVE 'COLPLTOC' TO FIO-PROG.
           PERFORM GNS-BUS-IDD.
           SORT GNSSRT
       COPY COLRSTOC.
           INPUT  PROCEDURE IS INP-SRT
           OUTPUT PROCEDURE IS OUT-SRT.
       FIN-MAIN.
           PERFORM GNS-PRO-END.

       INP-SRT SECTION.
      *---------------
       INI-INP-SRT.
           MOVE FIO-INP TO FIO-CMND.
           PERFORM COL-FIO-TOC.
       FST-INP-SRT.
      *<<<<
      *Busca Nombre de la Tabla.
           MOVE 'COL'  TO FIO-SIST.
           MOVE 'TOC'  TO TAB-COD-TTAB IN TAB.
           MOVE SPACES TO TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB.
           MOVE FIO-GET-KEY TO FIO-CMND.
           PERFORM GNS-FIO-TAB.
           IF FIO-STAT-OKS
               MOVE TAB-GLS-DESC IN TAB        TO WSS-GLS-DESC
           ELSE
               MOVE 'TABLA SIN REGISTRO PADRE' TO WSS-GLS-DESC.
      *Busca Responsable de la Tabla.
           IF TAB-COD-ATRN IN TAB > SPACES
               MOVE TAB-COD-ATRN IN TAB TO USR-COD-USER IN USR
               PERFORM BUS-USR
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO USR-GLS-DESC.
      *>>>>
           MOVE FIO-GET-FST TO FIO-CMND.
           PERFORM COL-FIO-TOC.
       LUP-INP-SRT.
           IF NOT FIO-STAT-OKS
              GO TO FIN-INP-SRT.
      *<<<<
      *BUS-TAB busca glosa de codigo en tabla
           MOVE 'TAB'               TO TAB-COD-SIST.
           MOVE 'TIO'               TO TAB-COD-TTAB IN TAB.
           MOVE TOC-COD-TOCR IN TOC TO TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB.
           PERFORM BUS-TAB.
           IF NOT FIO-STAT-OKS
               GO TO NXT-OUT-SRT
           ELSE
               MOVE TAB IN TAB TO TIO IN TIO.
      *BUS-MSC busca glosa de miscelaneo en tabla
           IF TOC-MSC-OPEC IN TOC > SPACES
               MOVE 'COL'  TO MSC-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'OPEC' TO MSC-COD-TMSC IN MSC
               MOVE TOC-MSC-OPEC IN TOC TO MSC-COD-CMSC IN MSC
               PERFORM BUS-MSC
               MOVE MSC-GLS-DESC IN MSC
               TO WSS-GLS-OPEC IN WSS-TOC
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO WSS-GLS-OPEC IN WSS-TOC.
      *BUS-MSC busca glosa de miscelaneo en tabla
           IF TOC-MSC-TCOL IN TOC > SPACES
               MOVE 'COL'  TO MSC-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'TCOL' TO MSC-COD-TMSC IN MSC
               MOVE TOC-MSC-TCOL IN TOC TO MSC-COD-CMSC IN MSC
               PERFORM BUS-MSC
               MOVE MSC-GLS-DESC IN MSC
               TO WSS-GLS-TCOL IN WSS-TOC
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO WSS-GLS-TCOL IN WSS-TOC.
      *BUS-TAB busca glosa de codigo en tabla
           IF TOC-COD-RECU IN TOC > SPACES
               MOVE 'TAB' TO TAB-COD-SIST
               MOVE TOC-COD-RECU IN TOC TO TAB-COD-TABL IN TAB
               PERFORM BUS-TAB
               MOVE TAB-GLS-DESC IN TAB
               TO WSS-GLS-RECU IN WSS-TOC
           ELSE
               MOVE SPACES TO WSS-GLS-RECU IN WSS-TOC.
      *>>>>
       MOV-INP-SRT.
       COPY COLRMTOC.
           RELEASE SRT.
       NXT-INP-SRT.
           MOVE FIO-GET-NXT TO FIO-CMND.
           PERFORM COL-FIO-TOC.
           GO TO LUP-INP-SRT.
       FIN-INP-SRT.
           MOVE FIO-CLO TO FIO-CMND.
           PERFORM COL-FIO-TOC.

       OUT-SRT SECTION.
      *---------------
       INI-OUT-SRT.
           IF PGM-STAT-SRT-MAL
               GO TO EXT-OUT-SRT.
           OPEN OUTPUT RPTTOC.
           CALL 'GNSPLHDR' USING RPT-VARI.
           INITIATE RPT-TOC.
           RETURN GNSSRT AT END
                GO TO FIN-OUT-SRT.
       LUP-OUT-SRT.
       GEN-OUT-SRT.
           GENERATE DL-TOC.
       NXT-OUT-SRT.
           RETURN GNSSRT AT END
                GO TO FIN-OUT-SRT.
           GO TO LUP-OUT-SRT.
       FIN-OUT-SRT.
           TERMINATE RPT-TOC.
           CLOSE RPTTOC.
       EXT-OUT-SRT.
           EXIT.

